title: Eurovision Song Contest 2010 - ESC - final

In case you missed it...

The final of Eurovision Song Contest 2010. Recorded from Swedish television. Chapter breaks at the beginning of each song.

NB: This DVD is more compressed than the semifinals, due to the fact that it was recorded onto a DVD5 and I had to fit in over 3 hours.
